abstract: The table was developed within the ReMAP project (Output tool). It shows, for each Member State (MS), the sea use names (from the EMODnet categories) that are present in their MSP.
title: ReMAP - Output - Sea Use by MS

abstract:
Left: Number of Zoning Elements (ZEs) for each MS. 

Right: Disjoint Index for each MS. A Disjoint Index of 0  indicates complete ZEs overlapping, while 1 indicates complete separation between ZEs.
title: ReMAP - Output - Nr ZEs & Disjoint Index
